	<title>Creating a Project</title>

	<p>To create a new project, the user must select "New" from the "File" menu. A pop up window opens up, and the <link xref="SBML">SBML</link> files (at least one) must be added to the project. Each <link xref="SBML">SBML</link> file represents a model that can be posteriorly deleted from this initial list(<link xref="mainWindow">main window</link>). Once all <link xref="SBML">SBML</link> files are added, and "OK" is pressed, <link xref="newEpithelium">new Epithelia</link> can be added to the project.</p>

